果有组件的话，越狱后能启动吗","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/778555","replies":27,"created_ts":1621675653,"created":"17:27:33","title":"企业微信有 Callkit 吗？怎样开启","author":"wangyanchen126","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/wangyanchen126","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8dbe2fdfad240721cee54aa93e55934a?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":778499,"node":"信息安全","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/security","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4f2/3670/260_mini.png?m=1621356666","description":"<p>有一些敏感数据（非密码）要客户在网页提交，网站是 https，我知道密码可以公钥加 sha1 再传输，反正私钥在我后端对比就好。\n但是非密码敏感数据，后台要能拿到原文的，请问\n1 ） https 了，前端还需要对称加密吗？\n2 ）需要的话，用什么方式来加密？网页源码能看到加密算法吗？</p>\n<p>谢谢。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/778499","replies":26,"created_ts":1621650399,"created":"10:26:39","title":"https 网页数据还需要另外加密吗","author":"fxrocks","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/fxrocks","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c4789761b4ba48cc45273478a5b8d7ea?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":778518,"node":"Python","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/python","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/8613/985e/90_mini.png?m=1620107162","description":"DigitalOcean 和 Vultr 官方都只提供了 Go 语言（ DO 还有 Ruby ）的 API 封装。为什么不是 Python ？ Python 不是运维第一语言么？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/778518","replies":25,"created_ts":1621658216,"created":"12:36:56","title":"为什么云计算厂商倾向于提供 Go 的 API 封装而不是 Python 的？","author":"theklf4","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/theklf4","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4992f9ff63c26b4694fd1d2ca4e805e5?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":778505,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1618811339","description":"<p>我和女票都是外地的，在深圳工作，这种情况如果要摆酒，兄弟们有什么建议吗？\n我能想到的是：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>在双方老家各摆一次。</li>\n<li>在深圳集中摆一次。</li>\n<li>先领证，等买了婚房再摆酒。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>现在遇到的困惑是，在老家摆酒会比较简单，不是女票想要的那种；在深圳摆，没房子，租的房子又比较小，不太方便；难道真的只剩选项 3 了吗？买婚房也不是一年半载能搞定，但是女票想快点摆酒，最近被这事搅得很是心烦，故来请教一下大家，想听听大家的建议。感谢。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/778505","replies":25,"created_ts":1621652665,"created":"11:04:25","title":"在外地怎么办婚礼？","author":"hao4857","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/hao4857","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d204/63c1/291866_mini.png?m=1596429905"},{"id":778497,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1618811339","description":"最近看了一些技术博客，逛了逛牛客网，感觉越来越多的人开始投入了这方面。<br /><br />有没有过来人聊聊这个，技术写作办博客或者公众号这种，能赚多少钱？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/778497","replies":25,"created_ts":1621650395,"created":"10:26:35","title":"技术写作能赚多少钱？","author":"mseasons","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/mseasons","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b025/ca5b/197257_mini.png?m=1582250585"},{"id":778567,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1618811339","description":"<p>正如大家知道的，马上 Google Photo 开始收费了。加上一加手机大氢亡了，我换成了 iPhone 。于是，买了个二手 Pixel 1，长期插着电源放在家里连接 WiFi 当作备份中转。</p>\n<p>于是，需要一个 iPhone 上照片自动传到 Pixel 的 DCIM/Camera 目录实现自动备份的方案。</p>\n<p>大家有推荐吗？谢谢。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/778567","replies":24,"created_ts":1621677920,"created":"18:05:20","title":"求一个 iPhone 照片自动传输到 Pixel 1 手机实现无限备份的方案","author":"atfa","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/atfa","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/81244b521d5b744af4100ca1ed9b6ab9?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":778469,"node":"iPhone","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_mini.png?m=1615111905","description":"<p>之前用小米，感觉右侧边滑动返回特好用\n现在 iphone 要从左侧滑动，总感觉手太短...\n有什么解决方式么</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/778469","replies":21,"created_ts":1621614180,"created":"00:23:00","title":"iPhone 返回手势好难用","author":"zooo","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/zooo","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d94b/542a/284698_mini.png?m=1555513487"},{"id":778539,"node":"生活","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/life","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785","de